  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb0\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The price of loaf of bread also shot up",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "With effect from yesterday (03), the price of a bunch of roti has been increased by Rs 100 and the prices of paratha, roti and rolls by Rs 10 to 15, the Canteen Owners Association said.",
        "Asela Sampath, president of the association, said that the price has been increased due to the increase in the price of wheat flour and its shortage."
      ],
